		{
			"portrait":"questioning",
			"text":"A pentagram?"
		},
		{
			"portrait":"gruff",
			"text":"Isn’t that the shape wizards use to cast evil spells?"
		},
		{
			"portrait":"exhausted",
			"text":"Yeah, Leo. It’s the shape wizards use to cast evil spells."
		},
		{
			"portrait":"exhausted",
			"text":"There’s no artistry or subtle craftsmanship involved. It’s just a shape, and it’s just <i>so</i> evil."
		},
		{
			"portrait":"gruff",
			"text":"Don’t get smart with me, kid. That thing’s for summonin' demons, right?"
		},
		{
