			"text":"You <i>can</i> use it to summon a demon, sure…"
		},
		{
			"portrait":"satisfied",
			"text":"But they- they’ve got a wide variety of applications, depending on the way you inscribe the-"
		},
		{
			"portrait":"gruff",
			"text":"You draw the shape different and it does different stuff?"
		},
		{
			"portrait":"exhausted",
			"text":"<i>You’re oversimplifying.</i>"
		},
		{
			"portrait":"unsure",
			"text":"Maybe, kid. Maybe."
		},
		{
