			"text":"I’m not here to gawk at how good your dead wizard buddies are at geometry, alright?"
		},
		{
			"portrait":"gruff",
			"text":"Tell me what that thing was for!"
		},
		{
			"portrait":"pensive",
			"text":"It, uh…"
		},
		{
			"portrait":"weirded",
			"text":"Well, I can’t really say, actually. It looks like it burnt up before they could finish it."
